        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued May 5 at 4:54PM MDT until May 5 at 5:30PM MDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 454 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 12 miles southwest
of Lovington, moving northeast at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Ping pong ball size hail and 60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles. Expect wind
damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Lovington.
</description>
        <instruction>A Tornado Watch remains in effect until 800 PM MDT for southeastern
New Mexico.

For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
